01:30:14.663 --> 01:30:16.132
I'm not so sure.

1714
01:30:16.265 --> 01:30:19.868
Well, yeah.
He and LeMarcus
have the same mother.


1715
01:30:20.003 --> 01:30:21.804
Yeah, they both grew up
in Virginia.


1716
01:30:21.937 --> 01:30:24.974
Reggie,
he played JUCO football,


1717
01:30:25.108 --> 01:30:26.809
but that fizzled out
after they cut him


1718
01:30:26.942 --> 01:30:28.944
for having
too many concussions.


